# General engineering

- Read `AGENTS.md` and relevant `docs/` before editing.
- Keep diffs small, typed, and test-backed.
- Do not claim unimplemented features in UI or docs.
- Placeholders need a clear TODO and intended responsibility.
- Run `npm run check` before finishing substantive work.
- Update `docs/decisions.md` and `CHANGELOG.md` when decisions or user-visible behavior change.
